urls.title: World Cup news - latest: Portugal manager hits out at Ronaldo strop
urls.description: Portugal manager Fernando Santos hits out at Cristiano Ronaldo's reaction after he was substituted in their final group game; France's protest about Antoine Griezmann's goal being ruled out against Tunisia is rejected; Brazil's players unfurl a Pele tribute after their 4-1 win.
